1
00:00:55,696 --> 00:00:57,736
[Splashing water]

2
00:00:59,283 --> 00:01:01,360
'When I was young...

3
00:01:01,453 --> 00:01:06,081
'l met this beautiful girl
by a lake.

4
00:01:06,167 --> 00:01:07,366
Ow! Hey!

5
00:01:09,545 --> 00:01:12,251
Scusi! Scusi!

6
